óŸParchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/commands/docs/date_now.mdŸ@bffd0483a59995ea6bd4fac89f3ce6f0aa2219865e1eec0bbad330fdfd0d2a45Øtitle: date nowë®Examples⁄oGet the current date and format it in a given format string.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> date now | format date "%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S"


```
Get the current date and format it according to the RFC 3339 standard.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> date now | format date "%+"


```
Get the time duration since 2019-04-30.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> (date now) - 2019-05-01


```
Get the time duration since a more specific time.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> (date now) - 2019-05-01T04:12:05.20+08:00


```
Get current time and format it in the debug format (RFC 2822 with timezone).
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> date now | debug


```
íêê⁄ûTitle: title: date now
Path: Examples
Content:
Get the current date and format it in a given format string.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> date now | format date "%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S"


```
Get the current date and format it according to the RFC 3339 standard.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> date now | format date "%+"


```
Get the time duration since 2019-04-30.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> (date now) - 2019-05-01


```
Get the time duration since a more specific time.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> (date now) - 2019-05-01T04:12:05.20+08:00


```
Get current time and format it in the debug format (RFC 2822 with timezone).
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> date now | debug


```
